Aikido Switzerland ist eine Dachorganisa: Aikido Switzerland is an umbrella organization and comprises various groups from Dojos. Each group is its own organization, but it must comply with the rules of Aikido Switzerland, which refer to the international regulations of the Aikido Switzerland Support Aikikai Hombu Dojo in Tokyo, note.
